PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784299698
OL,3,CArchbishop welcomes new Bishop of
OL,4,CDerry Michael Router
OL,6,FArchbishop Martin added: "I know that
OL,7,FBishop Michael will receive a warm
OL,8,Fwelcome from the people, priests and
OL,9,Freligious of Derry.
OL,11,F"Bishop Michael brings many gifts to
OL,12,Fhis new role. His assistance to me in
OL,13,Fthe governance and administration of
OL,14,Fthe Archdiocese of Armagh, as well as
OL,15,Fhis oversight of our Pastoral Team,
OL,16,Fyouth ministry and adult faith
OL,17,Fformation, has helped him gain
OL,18,Fvaluable leadership experience which
OL,19,Fhe will no doubt develop further in
OL,20,Fthe Diocese of Derry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784299698
OL,3,CArchbishop welcomes new Bishop of
OL,4,CDerry Michael Router
OL,6,F"Bishop Michael has a warm and
OL,7,Fwelcoming personality. He is a gifted
OL,8,Fpreacher and communicator who
OL,9,Fproclaims the Gospel with conviction.
OL,10,FHe has a natural pastoral instinct for
OL,11,Fthe care of the clergy, support of
OL,12,Freligious."
OL,14,FThe Archbishop also paid tribute to
OL,15,Fthe outgoing Bishop of Derry Donal
OL,16,FMcKeown.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784299698
OL,3,CArchbishop welcomes new Bishop of
OL,4,CDerry Michael Router
OL,6,FHe said: "I also take this opportunity
OL,7,Fto thank Bishop Donal McKeown and wish
OL,8,Fhim many blessings in his retirement.
OL,9,FA few months ago Bishop Donal
OL,10,Fcelebrated his silver jubilee as
OL,11,Fbishop, having spent thirteen years as
OL,12,FAuxiliary Bishop of Down and Connor
OL,13,Fand twelve years as Bishop of Derry.
OL,14,FHe retains his youthful hope and sense
OL,15,Fof mission, as well as his down-to-
OL,16,Fearth friendliness and authenticity.
OL,17,FBishop Donal continues to serve God
OL,18,Fand the Church with great generosity
OL,19,Fand a deep commitment to the Joy of
OL,20,Fthe Gospel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784299698
OL,3,CArchbishop welcomes new Bishop of
OL,4,CDerry Michael Router
OL,6,F"Bishop Donal's many years in
OL,7,Feducation kept him young at heart. He
OL,8,Fhas always seen the potential for
OL,9,Fyoung people, inspired by faith, to
OL,10,Fmake the world a more loving,
OL,11,Fforgiving and hope-filled place. He
OL,12,Fhas shown tremendous dedication to
OL,13,FCatholic education, rooted in Gospel
OL,14,Fvalues and centred on the development
OL,15,Fof the whole person: spiritually and
OL,16,Fmentally, as well as intellectually
OL,17,Fand physically.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
