PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784299698
OL,3,CArchbishop welcomes new Bishop of
OL,4,CDerry Michael Router
OL,6,FAt Episcopal Conference level, Bishop
OL,7,FDonal has brought great wisdom to the
OL,8,Fconference table, especially in the
OL,9,Ffields of Education, Pastoral Renewal
OL,10,Fand Faith Development. His command of
OL,11,Flanguages, including Italian, German
OL,12,Fand his native Irish tongue, has given
OL,13,Fhim a breadth of insight into culture,
OL,14,Fidentity and international thinking.
OL,16,FAt a human level Bishop Donal is a
OL,17,Fperson of genuine empathy, kindness
OL,18,Fand compassion - he is a true 'son of
OL,19,Fencouragement' and a caring pastor.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
